title: Lamb stew with rosemary dumplings
description: Lamb stew made with neck fillet is economical and extremely tasty, the rosemary dumplings add the perfect finish.
ingredients: 750g/1lb 10oz lamb neck fillet, cut into 2.5cm/1in cubes
salt and freshly ground black pepper
2 medium carrots, cut into large dice
1 medium swede, cut into large dice
